      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔发表言论后欧洲股市暂停；联合信贷银行跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/european-stocks-edge-up-after-powell-comments-unicredit-jumps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市变化不大，主要股的涨幅被汽车制造商的跌幅所抵消。投资者仔细考虑了好坏参半的财报以及美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔周末的言论，鲍威尔重申市场可能需要等到 3 月份之后才会降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/european-stocks-edge-up-after-powell-comments-unicredit-jumps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
